    <h2>Chào Mừng Đến Với HUFLIT</h2>
    
    <img
      src="https://github.com/hoadm-net/HTML_Exercises/blob/main/Lab02-Links-Images/assets/images/campus.webp?raw=true"
      alt="HUFLIT Campus"
      width="600"
